  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><br><br><br>🐔🌾 Bubble Chicken Farm 🌾🐔<br><br>Bubble Chicken Farm is a charming and creative simulator that blends pirate adventure with the magic of a farm, providing a unique and cozy experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/b0cba8f5825d18831ab2ffee1eeca58f.avif?t=1731767855\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>🏴‍☠️ Embark on Your Pirate Farming Journey 🏴‍☠️<br>Leave the pirate life behind and settle into the farm of your dreams! Your mission is to transform vast, unknown lands into a rural paradise filled with wonders.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/3ebe0c121355625d5339f23bf6433366.poster.avif?t=1731767855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/3ebe0c121355625d5339f23bf6433366.webm?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/3ebe0c121355625d5339f23bf6433366.mp4?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🐤 Bubble Chicken, Your Magical Companion 🐤<br>Discover the special powers of Bubble Chicken, your loyal companion. It will help you overcome obstacles, uncover secrets, and make your farm even more magical and special.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/dcf40f3747ba028d6d07a4e2d761630e.avif?t=1731767855\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>🌱 Pirate Farm Management 🌱<br>Take care of a variety of adorable animals and cultivate exotic plants. Personalize your farm to reflect your unique style and watch it flourish under your care. Blend pirate elements with farm life to create a truly unique place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/4e31afd68623fb0c6083d9673bdd0dbd.poster.avif?t=1731767855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/4e31afd68623fb0c6083d9673bdd0dbd.webm?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/4e31afd68623fb0c6083d9673bdd0dbd.mp4?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🛠️ Creative Construction 🛠️<br>Use your building skills to develop custom structures and create charming decorations. Transform your farm into a unique and welcoming place, with the freedom to design every detail to your liking.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/e1d250ed69b0cef2b78f00c0680ff7bb.poster.avif?t=1731767855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/e1d250ed69b0cef2b78f00c0680ff7bb.webm?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/e1d250ed69b0cef2b78f00c0680ff7bb.mp4?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/e7d3e69adaace14c3ea28275a449a94b.avif?t=1731767855\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>🌐 Online Mode 🌐<br>Connect with other players to share tips, trade resources, and collaborate on common projects. Alternatively, play offline for a more intimate and relaxing experience.<br><br>🚀 Pirate Adventure and Exploration 🚀<br>Explore new lands full of exciting quests, just like a true pirate! Discover fascinating locations and embark on a journey of discovery that will make your farm thrive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/b9b2228e79b6b85e51a335dc0bcbb919.poster.avif?t=1731767855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/b9b2228e79b6b85e51a335dc0bcbb919.webm?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691790/extras/b9b2228e79b6b85e51a335dc0bcbb919.mp4?t=1731767855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
